===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: jìntuìliǎngnán

===Idiom===
'''[[進退]][[兩難]]'''
# [[between a rock and a hard place]]
# [[in a bind]]; [[in a pickle]]
# describes an awkward situation where one does not know what to do

